            <title><![CDATA[News Wrap: Trump takes first trip on Air Force One gifted by Qatar]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/news-wrap-trump-takes-first-trip-on-air-force-one-gifted-by-qatar</link>
